OL,3,CWearable baby brain scanner finds
OL,4,Cearly emotional intelligence
OL,6,FFor the first time, scientists are
OL,7,Fable to map the whole brain of a baby
OL,8,Fat once whilst it is being
OL,9,Fentertained, ITV News Science
OL,10,FCorrespondent Martin Stew repots
OL,12,FMost parents would love to know what's
OL,13,Fgoing on inside their children's
OL,14,Fheads. With babies, it's almost
OL,15,Fimpossible.
OL,17,FNot only can they not speak, but to
OL,18,Fscan their brain often requires
OL,19,Fsedation and an MRI.
