OL,3,CWearable baby brain scanner finds
OL,4,Cearly emotional intelligence
OL,6,FThat's why scientists from UCL and
OL,7,FBirkbeck Toddler and Baby Lab have
OL,8,Fbeen trialing a new wearable brain
OL,9,Fscanner for babies.
OL,11,FIt works by shining harmless red light
OL,12,Fthrough the scalp and skull. The beams
OL,13,Freflected back from the brain record
OL,14,Flevels of blood flow which allows
OL,15,Fscientists to see which parts of the
OL,16,Fbrain are stimulated and when.
