OL,3,CWearable baby brain scanner finds
OL,4,Cearly emotional intelligence
OL,6,FFor the first time, they've been able
OL,7,Fto map the whole brain at once whilst
OL,8,Fthe baby is being entertained.
OL,10,FBy comparing scans from when the baby
OL,11,Fwas and was not engaged socially,
OL,12,Fscientists could see differences in
OL,13,Factivity in the prefrontal cortex.
OL,14,FThis suggests babies as young as five
OL,15,Fmonths old are displaying signs of
OL,16,Femotional intelligence.
OL,18,F"One of the things we see is much
OL,19,Fgreater interaction in social
OL,20,Fsituations." Professor Emily Jones
OL,21,Fshowed me.
