OL,6,F"Some areas of the brain are much more
OL,7,Factive when watching people singing to
OL,8,Fthem and talking to them than when
OL,9,Fthey are looking at toys."
OL,11,FIt's been a fascinating experience for
OL,12,FLaura Chatten, whose son Victor has
OL,13,Fbeen part of the trial.
OL,15,F"That's really interesting how early
OL,16,Fit is because they can't talk to us
OL,17,Fand they pick up on our queues.
