OL,3,CWearable baby brain scanner finds
OL,4,Cearly emotional intelligence
OL,6,F"It's so interesting to see it lit up.
OL,7,FHow the brain lights up. When you get
OL,8,Fthe feedback and they tell you what it
OL,9,Fmeans, that's really fascinating."
OL,11,FThe tech can be worn by babies as
OL,12,Fyoung as one month old.
OL,14,FStudying a range of ages and
OL,15,Fconditions. One of the most exciting
OL,16,Fuses could be to diagnose and monitor
OL,17,Fneurodiverse conditions like ADHD and
OL,18,Fautism.
